  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.graphics.drawable.Drawable.Callback, android.view.accessibility.AccessibilityEventSource, android.view.KeyEvent.Callback, android.view.ViewTreeObserver.OnPreDrawListener, AnimatedView, RippleView, ShadowView, AutoSizeTextView, RevealView, StateAnimatorView, TintedView, TouchMarginView, ValidStateView, VisibleView

    public class SearchEditText
extends EditText
    This implementation extends EditText directly and uses TextWatcher for tracking text changes. This class can be used to create new material search fields with drop down menus separated by a seam.
